<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.235.99140.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. A rooted Maximum Likelihood tree for Hosta Clade 1 reconstructed using MIG-seq data. Bootstrap values are indicated on internodes. Based on the Maximum Likelihood tree of 28 Japanese species (Fig. 1), H. gracillima is used as an outgroup." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/938503" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

